	: .zombie? .typeid@ THING_ZOMBIE = ;
	
	: defectchatter 1 4 rnd case 
	1 of sfx{ creepy 0.75 pitch! 800 1400 rnd d! } endof 
	2 of sfx{ creepy 0.6 pitch! } endof
